reviewText: This is an accurate biography as far as it goes.  It is a snapshot of the admiral's life.  I actually purchased a strictly audio book version on "I Tunes" for a few dollars.  I could listen to it on my "I Pod" while taking a walk.  It was well worth the small investment.  Thank You...
I liked this video.  I enjoyed the content and like the way it was put together.  I will watch it again.
